-- Renault to Consider China Expansion in New Strategic Plan, Les Echos Says
-- Albertina Torsoli
-- 2010-07-12T04:26:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/renault-to-consider-china-expansion-les-echos-reports.html

          
          
             Renault SA will consider expanding
in China, Les Echos reported, without saying how it obtained the
information. Growth in China is one of the questions the French
carmaker will face as it draws up a new strategic plan in 2011,
Les Echos said.  
          
          


  


        